SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://card.weibo.com/article/m/show/id/2309634270813917411315?_wb_client_=1&amp;object_id=1022%3A2309634270813917411315&amp;open_source=weibo_search&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=100103type%3D1%26q%3D%E7%99%BE%E6%97%A5%E6%97%A0%E5%AD%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcard.weibo.com%2Farticle%2Fm%2Fshow%2Fid%2F2309634270813917411315%3F_wb_client_%3D1%26object_id%3D1022%253A2309634270813917411315%26open_source%3Dweibo_search%26luicode%3D10000011%26lfid%3D100103type%253D1%2526q%253D%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2597%25A0%25E5%25AD%25A9&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=3d51ffac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://card.weibo.com/article/m/show/id/2309634270813917411315?_wb_client_=1&amp;object_id=1022%3A2309634270813917411315&amp;open_source=weibo_search&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=100103type%3D1%26q%3D%E7%99%BE%E6%97%A5%E6%97%A0%E5%AD%A9</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:35:33.000Z","msg":"有冇發覺啲黑暗歷史永遠大部份喺49年打後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c595298c786459190c809758a7dbb96e7bfa736b","tid":2499863,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b486212daa71fd5633a08bffbfe5ba4e32502a16","tid":2499863,"uid":104684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"癡撚線，聽到都毛骨悚然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"我諗日本侵華都冇玩到咁盡<br />\n<br />\n依個咁既垃圾國家幾時先肯摺埋"},{"pid":"ede403be8ee19b7ae18c2fa540be6ade25883b76","tid":2499863,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"回顧中共黑歷史系列：「山東百日無孩運動」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2499899\" data-auto-link target=\"_b